  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to Wenngrove!</strong></h2>Farm, fish, craft, and cast spells with your friends in this idyllic, magical multiplayer farming sim.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Magical World</strong></h2>Play as a Witch sent to investigate the disappearance of a fellow magical researcher, who was lost while exploring the nearby Wilds. Uncover the secrets hidden in the mysterious spellbook she left behind. Befriend the local townsfolk of Wenngrove, learn their trades and their stories, and make a beautiful home alongside your trusty Familiar.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/0ccfebc2c63db014a8643cc9bbbda82b.poster.avif?t=1765470089\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/0ccfebc2c63db014a8643cc9bbbda82b.webm?t=1765470089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/0ccfebc2c63db014a8643cc9bbbda82b.mp4?t=1765470089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Farm at the Homestead</strong></h2>The Homestead is your own space to customize and grow ingredients for your spells. Farm, craft and build furniture to make your hut into a home. Or maybe cook a big meal and have your friends over for a grand party - which may or may not include witchcraft!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/5ebbbee06b1b261109dfd169501b523c.poster.avif?t=1765470089\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/5ebbbee06b1b261109dfd169501b523c.webm?t=1765470089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/5ebbbee06b1b261109dfd169501b523c.mp4?t=1765470089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore With Friends</strong></h2>Customize your character and display your bewitching personality in Spellfarers. Learn new patterns and recipes to sew yourself a new outfit. Meet new friends along the way, create a coven, and work together to forage and discover all of what Wenngrove has to offer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/13845333aaa958472147530a595c8170.poster.avif?t=1765470089\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/13845333aaa958472147530a595c8170.webm?t=1765470089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/13845333aaa958472147530a595c8170.mp4?t=1765470089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Welcoming Community</strong></h2>Many hands make light work! Teaming up with other witches can make for easier foraging and stronger spells. Whether you prefer to gather together, or go solo, Wenngrove will always welcome you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/440649a4b2f527db91f1d607bd1dc7f2.poster.avif?t=1765470089\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/440649a4b2f527db91f1d607bd1dc7f2.webm?t=1765470089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/440649a4b2f527db91f1d607bd1dc7f2.mp4?t=1765470089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to Wenngrove!</strong></h2>Farm, fish, craft, and cast spells with your friends in this idyllic, magical multiplayer farming sim.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Magical World</strong></h2>Play as a Witch sent to investigate the disappearance of a fellow magical researcher, who was lost while exploring the nearby Wilds. Uncover the secrets hidden in the mysterious spellbook she left behind. Befriend the local townsfolk of Wenngrove, learn their trades and their stories, and make a beautiful home alongside your trusty Familiar.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/0ccfebc2c63db014a8643cc9bbbda82b.poster.avif?t=1765470089\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/0ccfebc2c63db014a8643cc9bbbda82b.webm?t=1765470089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/0ccfebc2c63db014a8643cc9bbbda82b.mp4?t=1765470089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Farm at the Homestead</strong></h2>The Homestead is your own space to customize and grow ingredients for your spells. Farm, craft and build furniture to make your hut into a home. Or maybe cook a big meal and have your friends over for a grand party - which may or may not include witchcraft!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/5ebbbee06b1b261109dfd169501b523c.poster.avif?t=1765470089\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1569420/extras/5ebbbee06b1b261109dfd169501b523c.webm?t=1765470089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"ht